Global Expandable Baton Market Insights
Expandable Baton Market size was valued at USD 0.89 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.1% from 2024 to 2030.

Expandable Baton Market Overview
The global expandable baton market is expected to witness significant growth over the forecast period. The market was valued at approximately USD 320 million in 2024 and is anticipated to reach USD 450 million by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 5.5%. The increasing demand for personal security equipment, coupled with law enforcement and military applications, is driving this growth. Additionally, the adoption of expandable batons by private security firms and various government agencies is expected to further propel market expansion. The market benefits from technological advancements in baton design, enhancing durability and performance.

